h1. ?: - the Elvis operator

h2. Purpose

It's a contraction of the standard Java ternary operator (<condition> ? <do-if-true> : <do-otherwise>) that uses the value from the condition if it evaluates to @true@ according to Groovy Truth, otherwise it uses the right-hand-side value.

h2. Examples

{code:java}
def name = person.name ?: "Unknown"
{code}

